### [PAY-20] POST /payments con teamId de equipo inexistente (esperado: 400 Bad Request)
# ResourceNotFoundException en PaymentService → capturada por controller → 400
POST {{host}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adm_token}}

{
  "teamId": 999999,
  "receiptUrl": "https://storage.example.com/fantasma.jpg"
